'''Master Gardener''' was a title of respect used by the [[Ho'Din/Legends|Ho'Din]] due to their renown for ecological and biological work. Much like the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]], the Ho'Din had ranks. Learners were taught by healers, who were in turn counseled by the Master, the most knowledgeable amongst them.

